flow.name: Add Records
flow.BPMNXML:
<definitions targetNamespace="http://www.activiti.org/test" expressionLanguage="http://www.w3.org/1999/XPath" typeLanguage="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:omgdi="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DI" xmlns:omgdc="http://www.omg.org/spec/DD/20100524/DC" xmlns:bpmndi="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/DI" xmlns:activiti="http://activiti.org/bpmn" xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns="http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/20100524/MODEL">
  <process isExecutable="true" name="Add Records" id="addRecords">
    <startEvent name="Start" id="startevent1"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="List Objects" id="task1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_list_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${listMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_add_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Show Record" id="usertask1"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Update Record" id="task4">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_create_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${createMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <userTask activiti:formKey="poi_confirm_form" activiti:assignee="${wf_currentAssignee}" name="Confirmation" id="usertask4">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:formProperty writable="false" expression="${wf_status}" type="string" name="Status" id="Status"/>
      </extensionElements>
    </userTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="task1" sourceRef="startevent1" id="flow1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="endevent1" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" id="done"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="task4" sourceRef="usertask1" id="flow9"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask1" sourceRef="task4" id="flow10"/>
    <endEvent name="End" id="endevent1"/>
    <exclusiveGateway default="done" name="Exclusive Gateway" id="exclusivegateway1"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="task4" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" id="more">
      <conditionExpression xsi:type="tFormalExpression">${wf_optionsOutcome == "more"}</conditionExpression>
    </sequenceFlow>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="exclusivegateway1" sourceRef="usertask4" id="flow14"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="List Objects" id="servicetask1">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_list_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${listMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="usertask4" sourceRef="servicetask1" id="flow15"/>
    <serviceTask activiti:class="plugins.facts" name="Read Dummy Object" id="servicetask2">
      <extensionElements>
        <activiti:field name="PluginKey">
          <activiti:string>poi_get_fact</activiti:string>
        </activiti:field>
        <activiti:field name="parameterMap">
          <activiti:expression>${getMap}</activiti:expression>
        </activiti:field>
      </extensionElements>
    </serviceTask>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="servicetask2" sourceRef="task1" id="flow16"/>
    <sequenceFlow targetRef="usertask1" sourceRef="servicetask2" id="flow17"/>
  </process>
  <bpmndi:BPMNDiagram id="BPMNDiagram_addRecords">
    <bpmndi:BPMNPlane id="BPMNPlane_addRecords" bpmnElement="addRecords">
      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_startevent1" bpmnElement="startevent1">
        <omgdc:Bounds y="50.0" x="250.0" width="35.0" height="35.0"/>
      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>

      <bpmndi:BPMNShape id="BPMNShape_servicetask2" bpmnElement="servicetask2">

      </bpmndi:BPMNShape>

    <sequenceFlow id="flow20" name="POST" sourceRef="exclusivegateway1" targetRef="POSTrec">
